definition: down/downwards/below/lower/later/next (week etc)/second (of two parts)/to decline/to go down/to arrive at (a decision, conclusion etc)/measure word to show the frequency of an action

sentences.english: Market economy system can be divided into upper organization and lower organization.
sentences.chinese: 市场经济结构分层包括下层组织和上层组织。

sentences.english: Women of middle and lower classer have been laboring in different trades and seeking for economic independence.
sentences.chinese: 中下层女子从事各种行业的劳动，谋求经济自立。

sentences.english: Extension agent, worker Low-level staff providing assistance and advice to farmers.
sentences.chinese: 人员向农民提供帮助和咨询的下层工作人员。

sentences.english: A weasel has soft under-fur protected by stiff, shiny guard hairs.
sentences.chinese: 鼬的柔软的下层绒毛，由坚硬明亮的针毛保护着。

sentences.english: By the 6th month, the subendothelial layer could be distinguished.
sentences.chinese: 内皮下层第6个月可辨认出来。

sentences.english: The lowest megalayer is the low-density block basement.
sentences.chinese: 最下层是低密度块体基底层。

sentences.english: Episode II also features Weequays both on Tatooine, and in the lower levels of Coruscant.
sentences.chinese: 在《第二集》里，塔图因和科洛桑下层也有威奎人。

sentences.english: So, where can I get the down-level one that you are using?
sentences.chinese: 那么，哪里可以得到下层的一所使用的？

sentences.english: An insulating layer is formed above the conductive underlayer.
sentences.chinese: 在导电下层上形成绝缘层。

sentences.english: If the cell dies, it leaves the underlying tissue exposed.
sentences.chinese: 如果细胞死亡，将会使下层的组织暴露。

sentences.english: Sergeants Swordsmen are professional warriors, drawn from the lower classes.
sentences.chinese: 长剑军士属于职业部队，其成员多来自社会下层平民。

sentences.english: Laying should avoid shocked the lower masonry.
sentences.chinese: 砌筑时应避免震惊下层砌体。

sentences.english: Objective To study the morphological characteristics and distribution of the cells in the subventricular zone(SVZ).
sentences.chinese: 目的观察侧脑室脑室下层细胞的形态及分布。

sentences.english: Sometimes the ring comes down and curves into the lower atmosphere.
sentences.chinese: 有时这个环会下降，弯入在气层的下层。

sentences.english: Some nitrergic nerve ganglions were observed in the muscle layer or in the submucosa along the side of the circular muscle layer.
sentences.chinese: 在肌层和粘膜下层靠近环行肌一侧可见到氮能神经节。

sentences.english: The main design challenge was the fact that this project was mainly underground.
sentences.chinese: 而项目的最大挑战在于这个电影院主要设计在地下层。

top floor/the top of a building
